original_title: ミリオンがいっぱい~AKB48ミュージックビデオ集~
overview: In just a few years, Japanese idol group AKB48 has been featured in music videos for 70 of their songs over the course of three years. Now, AKB48 fans have a chance to own 36 of those music videos (and some of their alternate versions) on the Million Ippai music video collection!
title: Million Ippai - AKB48 Music Video Collection -
